| ENAME | DEPTNO | GENDER |
+-------+--------+--------+
| Adam  |     50 | M      |
| Alice |     30 | F      |
| Bob   |     10 | M      |
| Eric  |     20 | M      |
| Eve   |     50 | F      |
| Grace |     60 | F      |
| Jane  |     10 | F      |
| Susan |     30 | F      |
| Wilma |        | F      |
+-------+--------+--------+
(9 rows)

!ok
